## PART I: MATHEMATICAL FOUNDATIONS

### 1.1 THE REFORMULATION: FROM SPECULATION TO RIGOR

#### Original Hypothesis (Conceptual)
"Ontological friction between relativistic and quantum time produces entropic collapse → dark matter emergence"

**Problems with Original:**
- "Ontological friction" has no mathematical definition
- "Entropic collapse" violates second law of thermodynamics
- No connection to measurable quantities
- Untestable framework

#### Reformulation (Rigorous)
"Quantum fields coupled to dynamic spacetime metric near horizons undergo decoherence due to tidal forces and entanglement with interior degrees of freedom. The generated von Neumann entropy, unable to couple to standard model fields, manifests as gravitationally-interacting energy density (dark matter)."

**Advantages of Reformulation:**
- ✅ Fully mathematical formalism (von Neumann entropy, decoherence rates)
- ✅ Respects thermodynamic laws
- ✅ Connects to measurable gravitational signatures
- ✅ Falsifiable predictions

